{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/DriveThruMain.gif?t=1731464988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Concept:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A simulation of running and expanding a drive-thru shop where players take orders, prepare various beverages and foods, manage supplies, and serve customers efficiently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameplay Elements: <br><br>1. Order Taking: <br>- Receive and input customer orders for both beverages and foods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/TakingOrder.gif?t=1731464988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>2. Preparation:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Choose the correct cup size and shape for beverages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Prepare food items as requested.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/MakePizzaOrder.gif?t=1731464988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>3. Customization: <br>- Customize your shop and prices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ProductPlace.gif?t=1731464988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4. Payment System: <br>- Process payments using cash, credit cards, or mobile payments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Input amounts, provide correct change, and complete transactions accurately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 5. Supply Management: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   - Monitor inventory and restock supplies to keep the shop well-stocked.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/TabletProducts.gif?t=1731464988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6. Growth and Expansion: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   - Improve and expand the shop by upgrading equipment, adding new menu items, and opening new locations. <br>- Invest profits wisely to enhance the shop's reputation and attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Objective: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Efficiently manage and grow the drive-thru, accurately fulfill orders, maintain adequate supplies, and build a positive reputation for your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game offers a dynamic and realistic experience of operating and expanding a drive-thru, managing a wide range of beverages and foods, handling diverse payment transactions, and ensuring a steady supply of goods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731464988","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731464988","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/b9165b9d4f0925cdfd0a70c664a21af568aff035/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731464988","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/b9165b9d4f0925cdfd0a70c664a21af568aff035/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731464988","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Wishlist Now</h1><p></p><br><h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/RoadmapUpdated.jpg?t=1731464988\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img